instructions: Klondike: build piles of the four suits from ace to king on the foundations, move the face up cards to a card of the next higher value if it is of the opposite color. Golf: remove all the cards from the tableau piles, cards may be moved from the tableau to the waste pile only if they are either one rank higher or one rank lower than the top card, regardless of suit.
